<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Application Received - MEDH</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .header-subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .application-details {
        background-color: #f7fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .detail-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }

      .detail-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .detail-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .detail-value {
        color: #2d3748;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .application-id {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .process-timeline {
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .timeline-title {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .timeline-steps {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .timeline-step {
        padding: 12px 0;
        border-left: 3px solid #e2e8f0;
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-left: 10px;
        position: relative;
      }

      .timeline-step:before {
        content: "";
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #667eea;
        position: absolute;
        left: -7px;
        top: 16px;
      }

      .step-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .step-description {
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      .contact-info {
        background-color: #edf2f7;
        border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .contact-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #2d3748;
        color: #a0aec0;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer-logo {
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .footer-links {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }

      .footer-links a {
        color: #667eea;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 10px;
      }

      .footer-links a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #718096;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-container {
          margin: 0;
          border-radius: 0;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 25px 20px;
        }

        .detail-row {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 5px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">📚 MEDH</div>
        <div class="header-subtitle">Learning Platform</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
          Dear
          {{name}},
        </div>

        <p>Thank you for applying to join our team at Medh! We've received your
          application for the
          <strong>{{position}}</strong>
          role and appreciate your interest in being part of our mission to
          transform skill development education.</p>

        <!-- Application Details -->
        <div class="application-details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Application ID:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">
              <span class="application-id">{{application_id}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Position Applied:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{position}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Application Date:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate
                submitted_at
                "MMMM DD, YYYY"
              }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Status:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">Under Review</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Please quote this Application ID ({{application_id}}) in all
            further communications.</strong></p>

        <p>Your application has been successfully registered in our system, and
          our hiring team is currently reviewing your qualifications and
          experience. We're committed to a thorough and thoughtful selection
          process to ensure mutual fit for both candidates and our organization.</p>

        <!-- Process Timeline -->
        <div class="process-timeline">
          <div class="timeline-title">📋 What you can expect moving forward:</div>
          <ul class="timeline-steps">
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Initial Review (1-2 days)</div>
              <div class="step-description">Our hiring team will evaluate your
                application against the role requirements</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Preliminary Interview</div>
              <div class="step-description">A brief conversation to discuss your
                background and interest in the role</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Technical Assessment (where applicable)</div>
              <div class="step-description">A skills evaluation relevant to the
                position</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Final Interview Round (shortlisted
                candidates)</div>
              <div class="step-description">An in-depth discussion with
                department leaders and potential team members</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Final Decision</div>
              <div class="step-description">Offer extended to the selected
                candidate</div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We aim to complete the initial review process within two weeks of
          your application date. If your qualifications align with our current
          needs, a member of our talent acquisition team will reach out to
          schedule the next steps.</p>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-title">📞 Need Immediate Assistance?</div>
          <p>If you have any questions about your application or the hiring
            process, please contact our talent team at
            <strong>careers@medh.co</strong>. Please reference your application
            ID in all communications.</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 77108 40696</p>
        </div>

        <p>🌟
          <strong>Explore Medh Further:</strong>
          While you wait, we encourage you to learn more about our mission,
          vision, and the impact we're making in the education space:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Visit our website:
            <a
              href="https://www.medh.co"
              style="color: #667eea;"
            >www.medh.co</a></li>
          <li>Follow us on
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/medh"
              style="color: #667eea;"
            >LinkedIn</a></li>
          <li>Explore our blog for insights into our teaching methodology and
            educational philosophy</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We appreciate your patience during our selection process and thank
          you for your interest in contributing to Medh's mission of empowering
          learners through quality skill development.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
          <strong>Best regards,</strong><br />
          HR & Talent Acquisition Team<br />
          <strong>MEDH Learning Platform</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-logo">MEDH</div>
        <div>Empowering the next generation of learners</div>

        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://www.medh.co/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
          |
          <a href="https://www.medh.co/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>
          |
          <a href="mailto:careers@medh.co">Contact HR</a>
        </div>

        <div class="disclaimer">
          <p>&copy;
            {{currentYear}}
            MEDH Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">This email confirms receipt of your job
            application. Our team will be in touch within 2 business days if
            your profile matches our requirements.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <strong>MEDH Learning Platform</strong><br />
            📧 careers@medh.co | 📞 +91 77108 40696<br />
            🌐
            <a
              href="https://www.medh.co"
              style="color: #667eea;"
            >www.medh.co</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>